Package Classes.Template

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Attribute
    Represents a general or subcategory-specific Attribute.
    Category
    Represents the broad category that the item belongs to.
    GeneralAttributes
    A set of Attributes that applies to all items.
    Measurement
    Represents a measurement that should be taken of an item in a given subcategory.
    Recommendation
    Represents a recommended value for an Attribute or other value like Size.
    Size
    Represents a Size option.
    Subcategory
    Represents the Subcategory of the Item.
    Template
    Represents a set of fields to be completed by the user.
